Package Intranet

Class Request

java.lang.Object
Intranet.Observable
Intranet.Request
All Implemented Interfaces:
Interfaces.Extractable, Serializable
public abstract class Request extends Intranet.Observable implements Interfaces.Extractable
The Request class used for getting response from some user, it will be send to the DataBase and after the observer can get it and decide to decline or approve this request. Also this class implements Extractable interface, so it can be passed to the TableBuilder to make the table with specified fields.
See Also:
Extractable, Serialized Form
